### SoftimProject API — příklady (VS Code REST Client / JetBrains HTTP client)
### Nastav @apiKey na svůj osobní klíč z /api-keys.

@baseUrl = https://softimproject-api.azurewebsites.net
@apiKey = spk_PASTE_YOUR_KEY_HERE
@projectId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@ticketId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Projekty (najdi projectId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Tickety v projektu (stránkovaně, s filtry)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/tickets?page=1&pageSize=25
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Detail ticketu
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/tickets/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Založení ticketu
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "title": "Nový ticket z API",
  "description": "Popis (Markdown).",
  "ticketPriorityId": null
}

### Úprava ticketu
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/tickets/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "ticketId": "{{ticketId}}",
  "title": "Upravený titulek",
  "description": "Aktualizovaný popis.",
  "ticketPriorityId": null,
  "taskStateId": null
}

### Smazání ticketu
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/tickets/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Worklogy (filtr na projekt/ticket/období)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/worklogs?projectId={{projectId}}&page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Jeden worklog
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/worklogs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Založení worklogu
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/worklogs
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "ticketId": "{{ticketId}}",
  "date": "2026-06-15",
  "hours": 1.5,
  "description": "Práce vykázaná přes API (min. 16 znaků).",
  "isBillable": true
}
